bicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1020081, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, (please) send blessings upon Ali the son of Musa whom You have accepted and through whom You have satisfied whomever of Your creatures that You wish. O Allah, as You have made him act as argument against Your creatures, undertake the mission by Your command, support Your religion, witness against Your servants, and as he acted sincerely towards them in secret and in open and called to Your way with wisdom and excellent exhortation, so also (please) bless him with the most favorite blessings that You have ever bestowed upon any of Your intimate servants and Your choice ones over Your creatures. Verily, You are All-magnanimous, All-generous.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Ali bin Moosa (a.s) par durood bhej keh jin ko Tu ne pasand farmaaya, Tu apni makhlooq mein se jis ko chahe pasand kar leta hai. Ay Ma’bood! Jis tarah Tu ne qaraar diya unko apni makhlooq par, hujjat qaaem kiya apne amr par, madad-gaar banaaya apne deen ka aur gawah banaya apne bando’n par aur jis tarah unho ne ayaa’n o naha’n (zaahir) unki khair khwaahi ki aur unko daanish-mandi aur behtareen naseehat ke saath Tere raaste ki taraf bulaaya usi tarah Tu bhi un par rehmat kar woh behtareen rehmat jo Tu ne makhlooqaat mein se apne waaliyo’n aur bar-guzido’n mein se kisi ek par ki hai, be-shak Tu bohot dene waala hai sakhi.", "Urdu": "اے معبود!علیؑ ابن موسیٰؑ پر درود بھیج کہ جن کو تو نے پسند فرمایا تو اپنی مخلوق میں سے جس کو چاہے پسند کر لیتا ہے اے معبود! جس طرح تو نے ان کو قرار دیا اپنی مخلوق پر حجت قائم کیا اپنے امر پر، اپنے دین کا مدد گار بنایا اور گواہ بنایا  اپنے بندوں پر اور جس طرح انہوں نے ظاہر و پوشیدہ طور پران کی خیر خواہی کی اور ان کو دانش مندی اور بہترین نصیحت کے ساتھ تیرے راستے کی طرف بلایا اسی طرح تو بھی ان پر رحمت کر وہ بہترین رحمت جو تو نے مخلوقات میں سے اپنے والیوں اور برگزیدوں میں سے کسی ایک پر کی ہے بے شک تو بہت دینے والا  سخی ہے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA A’LIYYIB-NE MOOSAL LAZIR TA-ZAIYTA-HU WA RAZZAIY-TA BEHI MAN SHE-TA MIN KHALQE-KA. ALLAAHUMMA WA KAMAA JA-A’L-TA-HU HUJJA-TAN A’LAA KHALQE-KA WA QAA-E-MAN BE-AMRE-KA WA NAASE-RAN LE-DEENE-KA WA SHAAHE-DAN A’LAA E’BAADE-KA WA KAMAA NASA-HA LAHUM FIS SIRRE WAL A’LAANE-YA-TE WA DA-AA’ ILAA SABEELE-KA BIL HIKMA-TE WAL MAW-E’ZA-TIL HASANA-TE FA-SALLE A’LAIHE AF-ZALA MAA SAL-LAIY-TA A’LAA AHA-DIN MIN AWLIYAA-E-KA WA KHEYA-RA-TE-KA MIN KHALQE-KA INNA-KA JAWAA-DOON KAREE-MOON.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى عَلِيِّ بْنِ مُوْسَى الَّذِي ارْتَضَيْتَهٗ وَرَضَّيْتَ بِهٖ مَنْ شِئْتَ مِنْ خَلْقِكَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ وَكَمَا جَعَلْتَهٗ حُجَّةً عَلٰى خَلْقِكَ وَقَائِمًا بِاَمْرِكَ وَنَاصِرًا لِدِيْنِكَ وَشَاهِدًا عَلٰى عِبَادِكَ وَكَمَا نَصَحَ لَهُمْ فِي السِّرِ وَالْعَلَانِيَةِ وَدَعَا اِلٰى سَبِيْلِكَ بِالْحِكْمَةِ وَالْمَوْعِظَةِ الْحَسَنَةِ فَصَلِّ عَلَيْهِ اَفْضَلَ مَا صَلَّيْتَ عَلٰى اَحَدٍ مِّنْ اَوْلِيَائِكَ وَخِيَرَتِكَ مِنْ خَلْقِكَ اِنَّكَ جَوَادٌ كَرِيْمٌ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "Arab